{"tid":2310341,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【震驚！】一男子當街被殺 疑因嘲笑阿仙奴","createTime":"2020-12-03T07:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T18:29:50.000Z","uid":45772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"282fff424d785f84b297352330cd37d252e2fc01","tid":2310341,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20201202/12474554/?cf=fb_hk_gp_soccer&amp;u=jay&amp;st=KDFOfR&amp;fbclid=IwAR29NmFYSWxejmM0f91gfxrJAfO9g010jhhPLHa4MwsP-JgWH1M0oY4pQCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F1%2F20201202%2F12474554%2F%3Fcf%3Dfb_hk_gp_soccer%26u%3Djay%26st%3DKDFOfR%26fbclid%3DIwAR29NmFYSWxejmM0f91gfxrJAfO9g010jhhPLHa4MwsP-JgWH1M0oY4pQCg&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=9f1bd299\" target=\"_blank\">https://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20201202/12474554/?cf=fb_hk_gp_soccer&amp;u=jay&amp;st=KDFOfR&amp;fbclid=IwAR29NmFYSWxejmM0f91gfxrJAfO9g010jhhPLHa4MwsP-JgWH1M0oY4pQCg</a><br />\n<br />\n據外媒《standardmedia》報導，一名堅尼亞男子在Naivasha地區的一家酒吧附近與他人發生衝突後，被石頭砸中頭部而不幸離世。據悉，這起衝突前雙方曾因阿仙奴與狼隊的比賽而發生爭吵。<br />\n<br />\n  該媒體稱，當地時間週日晚上，事件發生於Naivasha- Kirima路的Kinamba中心，在死者與朋友喝酒的酒吧之外幾米的一個加油站附近，而死者與兇手則是一起看球的朋友，當時死者嘲笑了身為阿仙奴球迷的兇手。當地時間週一早上，警方在街上發現了死者的屍體，並已經展開了對兇手的搜捕行動。<br />\n<br />\n  一位名叫彼得的目擊者稱，當時包括二人在內的一行人正在觀看酒吧內電視直播的足球賽，隨後雙方在比賽中攻入一粒入球後發生了爭吵。彼得表示：「雙方從爭吵升級為互相辱罵，後來死者被趕出酒吧，被兇手攻擊頭部後倒在地上失去了反應。」"},{"pid":"17c904259a268192ca24a5665eacb1cd57195ce1","tid":2310341,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">阿共奴</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"096f9574d0aa2fdc904cebbfeabbc98571e5f340","tid":2310341,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"邊撚到堅尼亞 係咪肯尼亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0df6a8bbe83e302a400b2bdb839a6e2a465e6af","tid":2310341,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"共仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ebda7b3a958eb4c40c416e98251e0a295e1bb0","tid":2310341,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"096f9574d0aa2fdc904cebbfeabbc98571e5f340","tid":2310341,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"邊撚到堅尼亞 係咪肯尼亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"肯亞呀戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d153bb4c40a4aedd4263349f9da9517a42c7d7","tid":2310341,"uid":129536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T18:29:50.000Z","msg":"KC一下撞低對面個力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}